Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.56,0:00:07.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高桥
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.22,0:00:14.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只说一次 你听好了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.65,0:00:20.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜欢你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.41,0:00:25.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天哪
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.72,0:00:37.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高桥
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.55,0:02:50.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们接吻了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.48,0:02:56.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对方是从春天开始一直喜欢着的男生
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.46,0:02:58.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然告白过一次
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.46,0:03:02.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,却得到不置可否的回应
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.82,0:03:06.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本来已经认为不可能了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.98,0:03:10.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.77,0:03:13.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜欢你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.88,0:03:27.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇迹般地...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.15,0:03:31.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界一下变了色彩
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.96,0:03:37.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为矢野施了魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.48,0:03:46.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好...早上好...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.67,0:03:50.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一晚都没睡好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.69,0:03:54.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.14,0:03:57.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小七 看上去很高兴嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.11,0:04:01.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办 都被别人看出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.60,0:04:03.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直到昨天为止
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.04,0:04:08.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他都只是嘴巴不饶人 总是斗嘴的同班同学
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.27,0:04:11.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天要用什么样的表情面对他呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.20,0:04:13.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我考虑了一整夜
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.72,0:04:23.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.75,0:04:24.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早...早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.09,0:04:33.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.50,0:04:35.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成为朋友真的很不错
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.80,0:04:36.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.25,0:04:40.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不...不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.88,0:04:44.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无法直视他的脸
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.38,0:04:52.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然这么说 但是他和平时没什么两样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.95,0:04:58.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小水...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.25,0:05:01.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你和矢野接吻了 是真的?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.76,0:05:04.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,何时发生的?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.15,0:05:06.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可饶恕 从实招来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.82,0:05:09.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会吧 被别人看见了?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.04,0:05:12.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么? 你们开始交往了?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.26,0:05:16.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦? 啊 对哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.42,0:05:19.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思 以后不能再当你的恋爱顾问了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.52,0:05:22.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过你们要是分手的话 我倒可以替你加油
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.79,0:05:23.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,随时可以找我商量哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.84,0:05:30.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交往...可是矢野什么都没说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.93,0:05:32.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也没有短信
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.85,0:05:35.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起来他从来没有给我发过短信
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.25,0:05:40.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,越想越觉得生气
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.36,0:05:42.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.84,0:05:46.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他来了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.14,0:05:49.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高桥
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.39,0:05:51.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.94,0:05:54.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,星期六庆功宴
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.80,0:05:58.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 这样啊 这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.86,0:06:01.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你今天是不是有点神志恍惚
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.69,0:06:03.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 我昨天没有睡好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.32,0:06:04.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完了...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.56,0:06:06.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.41,0:06:09.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为接吻所以睡不着 真是个笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.01,0:06:12.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来只是普通的联络事项
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.25,0:06:14.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么我重述一遍
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.58,0:06:16.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天3点开委员会
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.03,0:06:18.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,星期四开实行委员反省会
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.94,0:06:19.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,星期六庆功宴
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.64,0:06:22.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天三点开委员会
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.39,0:06:23.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,星期二...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.36,0:06:23.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是星期四
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.22,0:06:25.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 星期四反省会
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.42,0:06:30.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天3点委员会 12点午休 星期六庆功宴
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.80,0:06:35.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天3点委员会 12点午休 星期四庆功宴
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.41,0:06:37.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋 星期六庆功宴
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.30,0:06:38.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天4点看电影
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.95,0:06:42.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么嘛 今天委员会 星期四反省会
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.68,0:06:44.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,星期六庆功宴 今天4点看电影
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.13,0:06:46.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 都记住了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.45,0:06:52.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天 4点...4点...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.00,0:06:56.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,4点...看电影...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.65,0:06:59.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.91,0:07:04.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我从一大早开始就心跳超快
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.66,0:07:06.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他为什么总是那么笃定的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.09,0:07:09.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要露出可爱的笑容啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.04,0:07:14.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,松了一口气 睡意终于侵袭而来了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.42,0:07:19.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 今天矢野终于主动对着我笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.25,0:07:24.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是谎言 不是幻觉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.02,0:07:27.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天的事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.74,0:07:36.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 她怎么还在睡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.23,0:07:39.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天都睡了一整天了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.35,0:07:43.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小七 3点开委员会啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.89,0:07:48.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,约会 约会 怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.65,0:07:53.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(2000,5000)\1c&H6A00D5&\move(420,450,370,390)}约会
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.41,0:07:50.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好紧张哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.60,0:07:57.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.42,0:08:03.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 已经那么晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.63,0:08:09.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,委员会...糟糕...早就结束了...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.66,0:08:15.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会...不会吧 矢...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.17,0:08:22.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回去了...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.77,0:08:26.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你终于醒了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.59,0:08:33.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还没回去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.96,0:08:38.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么还没回去 我替你去开委员会了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.87,0:08:42.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还帮你记了笔记
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.91,0:08:47.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有问卷调查 在班会上让同学填好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.51,0:08:48.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个下星期交
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.92,0:08:52.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.53,0:08:55.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你帮我去开会了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.63,0:08:57.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 我不是刚跟你说过
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.73,0:09:00.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真...真不敢相信
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.55,0:09:05.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个矢野 超怕麻烦超爱偷懒的矢野
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.44,0:09:15.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还能去看电影吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.07,0:09:26.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.91,0:09:31.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看电影 喝茶 可能还要吃饭
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.31,0:09:32.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,钱够不够呢...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.87,0:09:34.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系 我带钱了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.89,0:09:37.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会还的 明天一定还
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.72,0:09:38.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.68,0:09:39.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 一定要还
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.20,0:09:49.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有空座
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.12,0:09:50.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你坐吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.36,0:10:04.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还是站着吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.06,0:10:06.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,过一会儿会很挤的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.92,0:10:07.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要紧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.75,0:10:12.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.60,0:10:13.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.49,0:10:18.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总觉得...全身都在用力
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.33,0:10:20.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放轻松 放轻松
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.63,0:10:26.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你喝什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.09,0:10:29.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯...嗯...可可吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.73,0:10:31.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.50,0:10:31.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.97,0:10:33.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像人很少
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.67,0:10:36.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 应该说奶茶的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.34,0:10:41.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 又太用力了 放轻松 放轻松
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.61,0:10:47.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,矢野 你喜欢看电影吗 我从来都不知道哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.73,0:10:50.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为电影院很暗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.14,0:10:51.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.22,0:10:56.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本没听懂
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.24,0:11:01.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以把手放在这里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.82,0:11:02.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以啊 请放
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.78,0:11:09.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高桥累了的话也可以把手放这里哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.72,0:11:10.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.95,0:11:11.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.35,0:11:29.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,旁边的座位比想象中的还要近
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.75,0:11:39.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,电影讲了一个女人总是和喜欢的人擦肩而过
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.57,0:11:45.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 又来了 快让他们相遇呀
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.54,0:11:49.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于在一起了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.43,0:12:05.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手指体操
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.23,0:12:23.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没...没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.40,0:12:28.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他一直留了一半的位置
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.05,0:12:53.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两个人相互喜欢 真的很美好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.80,0:13:04.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小水 小高的 我们的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.98,0:13:05.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家好 我叫水口
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.18,0:13:06.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是永见
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.14,0:13:08.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很快就要开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.40,0:13:08.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.06,0:13:10.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么嘛 那个七美
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.39,0:13:11.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我大吃一惊啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.94,0:13:16.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,七美究竟什么时候开始喜欢他的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.47,0:13:17.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了好了 水口 冷静点
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.78,0:13:20.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 真是的 以后再也不当你的恋爱顾问了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.64,0:13:23.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我就是不能不管七美
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.92,0:13:24.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.22,0:13:26.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 但是 我绝对不会原谅你的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.11,0:13:28.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就这样 请继续欣赏下半集
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.07,0:13:32.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,电影真好看
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.77,0:13:33.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.42,0:13:33.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.10,0:13:35.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最后一幕真感人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.18,0:13:37.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,矢野觉得哪里最好看
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.81,0:13:38.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.76,0:13:41.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得...牵手的地方最好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.24,0:13:48.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我今天情绪太亢奋了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.72,0:13:51.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,矢野看上去和平常不一样
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.92,0:13:56.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说话的方式 动作 连声音的起伏
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.97,0:13:59.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都好像和平时不一样
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.51,0:14:01.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,困了么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.78,0:14:03.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.91,0:14:06.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像硬拖着你来 真不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.23,0:14:08.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃完就回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.15,0:14:14.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,矢野 你为什么那么体贴
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.21,0:14:16.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 什么为什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.96,0:14:18.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.07,0:14:20.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我本来就很体贴吧 怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.10,0:14:24.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是啊 因为我觉得怪怪的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.92,0:14:27.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前你一直欺负我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.67,0:14:30.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在突然像变了一个人似的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.83,0:14:34.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说喜欢我之前你都没有喜欢我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.59,0:14:39.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,变了的人是你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.06,0:14:40.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.07,0:14:43.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女朋友和同班同学是不一样的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.16,0:14:47.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高桥 对我来说你已经是和以前不同的人了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.71,0:14:52.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是说...女朋友...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.28,0:14:54.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.85,0:14:55.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.20,0:14:56.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.78,0:15:02.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是说 高桥已经是我的自己人了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.75,0:15:04.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己人?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.18,0:15:10.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 除了自己以外的人 还有自己人和外人之分吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.42,0:15:13.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊 好奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.10,0:15:17.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会怪吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.61,0:15:20.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.92,0:15:27.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我现在 突然好想 把矢野紧紧抱住
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.57,0:15:37.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\1c&000000&}喜气洋洋 两人服饰打扮计划
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.57,0:15:37.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\1c&000000&}\N今\N年\N和\N他\N的\N圣\N诞\N节\N 与\N众\N不\N同
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.25,0:15:40.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,往年我一向与这种活动无缘
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.06,0:15:42.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今年就不一样了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.18,0:15:46.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但问题是矢野的品位好像比我高啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.87,0:15:49.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要用心点 不能让矢野觉得我土
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.21,0:15:51.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这可是很费力的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.11,0:15:54.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男孩子喜欢怎么样的约会呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.33,0:15:58.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.29,0:16:00.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.42,0:16:07.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,矢野有时没事也会靠近我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.05,0:16:11.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在没有其他人的时候 像猫一样
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.32,0:16:16.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,矢野 圣诞节有什么想要的礼物吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.97,0:16:17.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要小七
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.11,0:16:18.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈哈哈
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.74,0:16:22.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你认真地回答嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.60,0:16:26.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\1c&H4F2700&\pos(462,350)}其\N实\N非\N常\N认\N真
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.27,0:16:27.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沙司
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.17,0:16:28.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是矢野
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.97,0:16:30.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝对沙司
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.69,0:16:32.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 酱油
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.63,0:16:32.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难怪最近他都不怎么和我们出去呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.83,0:16:33.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沙司
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.93,0:16:34.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,酱油
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.60,0:16:35.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沙司
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.40,0:16:37.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是说过要酱油的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.92,0:16:38.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 竹内
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.96,0:16:43.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好久不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.38,0:16:44.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去厕所
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.01,0:16:47.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们在争什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.56,0:16:51.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎...吃荷包蛋要沾酱油还是沙司
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.98,0:16:53.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呵呵 两个笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.45,0:16:57.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有啊 不是很好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.14,0:16:58.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿嘿
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.38,0:17:04.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沾酱油 想和别人一起分享的时候一定要用酱油
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.38,0:17:04.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs30}注：酱油和しよう(一起做)发音相似
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.96,0:17:06.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要在那里炫耀
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.24,0:17:10.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然有种似曾相识的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.19,0:17:16.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的没想到你竟然那么笨
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.80,0:17:19.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么孩子气
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.22,0:17:21.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去吃比萨吧 比萨
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.85,0:17:24.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 你怎么那么有钱
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.64,0:17:26.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明没有在打工
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.83,0:17:28.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为要多少父母都会给我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.33,0:17:31.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.31,0:17:34.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我爸妈好小气 都不肯帮我加零用钱
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.90,0:17:37.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我家是向父母要钱才算孝顺
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.87,0:17:45.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来牵手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.43,0:17:52.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,矢野的手 好温暖
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.27,0:17:57.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此每当我触到他的手
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.52,0:18:00.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,内心就会有种痛痛的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.68,0:18:05.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的手为什么这么冷
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.90,0:18:08.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女人都有寒冷症吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.97,0:18:14.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,矢野 礼物你要什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.92,0:18:17.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 当然不包括生物
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.76,0:18:23.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么都不要啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.40,0:18:24.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.89,0:18:30.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,矢野 一定注意到我零用钱少
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.82,0:18:33.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定在替我着想吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.40,0:18:37.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可我还是想送礼物给他
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.56,0:18:40.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有高桥在就可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.12,0:18:44.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 糟糕
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.63,0:18:45.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.69,0:18:47.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 说出来真不好意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.30,0:18:49.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 一口气说出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.76,0:18:51.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正都说了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.58,0:18:54.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.65,0:19:16.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今年的雪下得很早
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.23,0:19:26.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我的心却暖暖的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.44,0:19:31.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且 觉得自己变漂亮了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.82,0:19:32.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为恋爱?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.36,0:19:35.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗 他对女孩子的品味太糟糕了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.80,0:19:38.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丑八怪
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.80,0:19:39.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丑八怪还那样
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.16,0:19:40.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真火大
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.00,0:19:44.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近的年轻人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.30,0:19:48.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她们在嫉妒 不要介意
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.09,0:19:52.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 丑八怪是在说我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.97,0:19:56.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来我已经可以让人嫉妒了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.53,0:20:01.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.46,0:20:10.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有很多女孩子会哭吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.28,0:20:16.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要什么圣诞礼物?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.73,0:20:18.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不需要
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.89,0:20:22.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,矢野喜欢雪
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.47,0:20:26.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是丑八怪吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.38,0:20:34.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丑八怪应该还要更丑一些
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.48,0:20:37.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是美女吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.86,0:20:41.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美女 应该还要再漂亮一些
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.06,0:20:43.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了 你真直接
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.82,0:20:48.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,矢野喜欢我什么地方
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.15,0:20:52.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为你很可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.25,0:20:58.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么有时候会变得不安
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.07,0:21:00.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高桥 手借下
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.21,0:21:23.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一触到矢野温暖的手 我的内心便痛痛的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.44,0:21:26.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,决定了 圣诞节礼物
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.67,0:21:29.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要你答应我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.09,0:21:34.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永远不离开我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.99,0:21:49.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝对 绝对 绝对 不要背叛我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.03,0:21:55.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老实说 我也不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.90,0:22:01.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我从来没有想过还会和女孩子交往
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.51,0:22:06.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是真的真的喜欢我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.71,0:22:08.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.10,0:22:13.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了那样的小事
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.45,0:22:16.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小事...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.46,0:22:23.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她就和喜欢的男人一起死了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.34,0:22:27.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我绝对不会同情她
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.43,0:22:47.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像拼图的碎片
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.62,0:22:52.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一块一块地拼成了完整的图
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.40,0:23:19.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱恋 第一次了解这个词的含义
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.22,0:23:21.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在15岁的冬天
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.81,0:25:07.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,矢野拥着我
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.16,0:25:11.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,矢野的手抚摸着我的背
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.45,0:25:16.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后 矢野的手伸向了我的胸...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.22,0:25:19.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.21,0:25:19.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.99,0:25:21.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:22.32,0:25:24.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不过是个被抛弃的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.31,0:25:27.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们两姐妹 真是差劲透顶
Dialogue: 0,0:25:28.21,0:25:31.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别把我和她相提并论

